Los misterios de la vida,

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:10.160
Trate de no verlos claramente.

00:13:11.960 --> 00:13:14.560
Cierra los ojos,

00:13:15.880 --> 00:13:17.760
No respondas.

00:13:20.080 --> 00:13:23.760
